		<author><name><![CDATA[tzuk]]></name></author>
		<updated>2013-05-25T11:01:12-04:00</updated>

		<published>2013-05-25T11:01:12-04:00</published>
		<id>https://forums.sandboxie.com/phpBB3/viewtopic.php?t=15536&amp;p=90090#p90090</id>
		<link href="https://forums.sandboxie.com/phpBB3/viewtopic.php?t=15536&amp;p=90090#p90090"/>
		<title type="html"><![CDATA[[.09] Removed Low-Level and Hardware Access Settings]]></title>

		
		<content type="html" xml:base="https://forums.sandboxie.com/phpBB3/viewtopic.php?t=15536&amp;p=90090#p90090"><![CDATA[
I removed the Low-Level Access and Hardware Access settings pages from the Sandbox Settings window in version 4.01.09.<br>Reminder screenshot:<br><br><a href="http://www.sandboxie.com/index.php?RestrictionsSettings#lowlevel" class="postlink">http://www.sandboxie.com/index.php?Rest ... s#lowlevel</a><br><a href="http://www.sandboxie.com/index.php?RestrictionsSettings#hardware" class="postlink">http://www.sandboxie.com/index.php?Rest ... s#hardware</a><br><br>With version 4, many of these settings do not function correctly anymore, that is to say, they no longer make it possible for a program in the sandbox to do stuff outside the sandbox.<br><br>I feel these were rather esoteric settings that saw little use, so I don't t think they justify the time investment to make them work in version 4.  Some of them are even incompatible with the way things work under the hood in version 4.<br><br>I would point out that I feel the setting "Permit programs in this sandbox to simulate keyboard and mouse input" was perhaps used mostly to get rid of message <a href="http://www.sandboxie.com/index.php?SBIE1304" class="postlink">SBIE1304</a> Blocked simulated keyboard or mouse input by process program.exe.  So in version 4.01.09 Sandboxie no longer issues message SBIE1304.<br><br>Please note that behind the scenes Sandboxie still recognizes at this time some of these settings, if they appear in Sandboxie.ini.  This may change in the future.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.sandboxie.com/phpBB3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3">tzuk</a> — Sat May 25, 2013 11:01 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
